6000|$|... "But we are {{increasing}} rapidly--your sister, <b>Hare-Lip,</b> already has four children. We {{are increasing}} rapidly and making {{ready for a}} new climb toward civilization. In time, pressure of population will compel us to spread out, and a hundred generations from now we may expect our descendants to start across the Sierras, oozing slowly along, generation by generation, over the great continent to the colonization of the East--a new Aryan drift around the world.|$|E
